OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FThousands of homes without 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fwater on Christmas Day     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, About 5,000 houses in East Renfrewshire
OL,6, were without water on Christmas Day,   
OL,7, with some still cut off on Boxing Day. 
OL,9,FScottish Water said supply was affected
OL,10,Fby an "operational issue" at Picketlaw 
OL,11,FWater Treatment Works on 25 December.  
OL,13,FIt said the fault was fixed but people 
OL,14,Fin the Newton Mearns, Giffnock,        
OL,15,FThornliebank and Clarkston areas may   
OL,16,Fstill only have "intermittent" water   
OL,17,Fsupplies over Boxing Day.              
OL,19,FBottled water collection points have   
OL,20,Fbeen set up for affected households.   
